definitions.definition: An act of drawing back or removing ; a removal , a withdrawal or withdrawing .
Synonym of withdraught ( “ a dismissal of a lawsuit with prejudice based on a plaintiff 's withdrawal of the suit ; a retraxit ; also, a fine imposed on a plaintiff for such a dismissal ” ) .

main_definition: An act of drawing back or removing ; a removal , a withdrawal or withdrawing .
